metadata.name: Hong Kong l 香港
metadata.description:
Lonely city in Hong Kong.

An empty city repeating daily life!
When you think life is boring.
I get helpless. nevertheless
that you can keep repeating,
Eventually, you will be able to do well.

Life is a series of challenges!
It has meaning in itself.

(I expressed the complex city sensibility with pen and ink on paper.)

2094 x 2304, mp4
